      <title>据称，阿达尼丰益因美国贿赂指控推迟出售股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/adani-wilmar-said-to-defer-stake-sale-amid-us-bribery-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在美国对亿万富翁创始人高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 提出贿赂指控后，阿达尼企业有限公司 (Adani Enterprises Ltd.) 和丰益国际有限公司 (Wilmar International Ltd.) 推迟了出售其印度食品合资企业至少 12% 股份的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/adani-wilmar-said-to-defer-stake-sale-amid-us-bribery-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 08:41:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
