      <title>津巴布韦货币动荡缓解，通胀降温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/-zwg-usd-zimbabwe-inflation-rate-falls-as-zig-currency-turmoil-eases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦的月度通胀率四个月来首次放缓，困扰该国以黄金为支撑的货币 ZiG 的波动性出现消退的迹象。]]></description>
