      <title>新加坡交易员对 11 亿美元欺诈行为不认罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/singapore-businessman-faces-trial-over-1-1-billion-nickel-scam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名前会计师被指控实施了震惊新加坡商界的数十亿美元的镍币诈骗案，周二他对包括洗钱在内的 42 项指控表示不认罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/singapore-businessman-faces-trial-over-1-1-billion-nickel-scam</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 05:01:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本 SBI 跟随野村证券公布阿达尼基金风险敞口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/japan-s-sbi-follows-nomura-in-disclosing-adani-funds-exposure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着印度企业集团阿达尼集团丑闻的余波蔓延，SBI 控股公司已与野村控股公司和其他日本金融公司一起公布了其共同基金对阿达尼集团公司证券敞口的详细信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/japan-s-sbi-follows-nomura-in-disclosing-adani-funds-exposure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 01:28:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：特朗普关税威胁导致美元上涨、股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，美国将对中国、墨西哥和加拿大征收额外关税，这加剧了人们对其“美国优先”政策的担忧，随后美元走强，股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 22:35:23 GMT</pubDate>
